  "Dlg_UpdatedBody": "Welcome back! UCM has been updated.\n\nWhat's new:\n- Sacred God Mode: your edits are permanently protected from Quick/Fine Tune rebuilds\n- Lock-on Auto-Rotate toggle (credits to @sillib1980)\n- Green indicators for sacred values in God Mode\n- Fix: sacred values now correctly included in Install and all exports\n\nYour presets and settings have been preserved.",
