  "Tutorial_Step1Desc": "This is your preset sidebar. Click Browse to download official UCM presets and community presets. Your own presets and imports also appear here. Click any preset to load it.",
  "Tutorial_Step1Title": "Your Presets",
  "Tutorial_Step2Desc": "UCM Quick for fast changes, Fine Tune for deep control over every camera state, and God Mode for raw XML editing. Changes sync across all three tiers automatically.",
  "Tutorial_Step2Title": "Three Editing Tiers",
  "Tutorial_Step3Desc": "Adjust camera distance, height, horizontal shift, field of view, lock-on zoom, and camera behaviour. The live preview updates as you tweak.",
  "Tutorial_Step3Title": "Camera Settings",
  "Tutorial_Step4Desc": "The camera preview shows character framing and distance. The field of view diagram shows the FoV cone from above. Both update in real time as you adjust settings.",
  "Tutorial_Step4Title": "Live Preview",
  "Tutorial_Step5Desc": "Export your settings as JSON for mod managers, XML, 0.paz, or .ucmpreset to share with others. Or click Install to Game to apply directly to your game files.",
  "Tutorial_Step5Title": "Export & Install",
  "Tutorial_Step6Desc": "I've dedicated way too much time to this project. If UCM saved you hours of camera frustration, consider buying me a coffee. Or don't. I'll keep making it anyway. But coffee helps.",
  "Tutorial_Step6Title": "One More Thing..."
}